   This scene opens with Hedge, Sniper, amd Ga-ga-bot in the same seats as 
they were in before.  Sitting next to Sniper is Sqril.  On the left of 
Hedge, in the 2nd in command chair, is Pyrotic.  In the chair Pyrotic was in 
before is now Ostick.  Thug-bot is sitting next to Ostick.  It is 43 minutes 
after 'Cybertron Mob(part 2)'.

   "Ga-ga-bot, how much more time before we arrive on Earth?" Hedge ask 
Ga-ga-bot.

   "Umm... Well, 2 and a half minutes."  Ga-ga-bot says.

   "Good, Sniper, Scan for Predacon frequencies when we land, we need to 
make a few allies.  Sqril, Check the computer to make sure that all the 
autoguns are ready to be set up when we land.  Ostick, make sure our shields 
are ready, and Thug-bot, make sure the flamethrowers are working." Hedge 
says.

   "Yeah, make sure they burn private."  Pyrotic says.

   It takes a few seconds while they check for the information that was 
asked for.

   "We have like 60 autoguns like so ready." Sqril says.

   "Good.  We will set up 30 of them and have the 30 others for spares." 
Hedge says.

   "Everything is working with the shields."  Ostick says.

   "And the flamethrowers are burning."  Thug-bot says.

   "Excellent."  Hedge says.

   "Whoa, umm... Hedge, this computer says we have a bomb in the engine 
room." Ga-ga-bot says.
